                            Under a Baleful Sky
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:90%;"><strong>&#171; <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/thirty-pieces-of-silver-plus-inflationary-costs">Previous Tale</a> | <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/maim-the-sky-slay-the-sun-hub">Maim the Sky, Slay the Sun</a> | <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/quarterly-performance-review">Next Tale</a> &#187;</strong></span></p>
